s=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">🐰作者简介：一位普通高校的在校学生，致力于提高自己的编程能力。\n🍌个人主页：[比昨天强一點的博客_CSDN博客-领域博主](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;c-p-p.blog.csdn.net&#x2F; &quot;比昨天强一點的博客_CSDN博客-领域博主&quot;)\n🍍系列专栏：[C语言从0到精通_比昨天强一點的博客-CSDN博客](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.csdn.net&#x2F;m0_63125842&#x2F;category_12057278.html &quot;C语言从0到精通_比昨天强一點的博客-CSDN博客&quot;)\n🏷️学习格言：无人问津的日子，最是提高自己的好时机。</code></pre></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<pre><code>     如果你在使用Clion进行debug时出现这种情况\n</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/9cf9801c14c5484fa7743e521f3489a9.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/f448e93253d24bc9bfcaea2a0c66ffe0.png\">显示找不到host</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">那么很有可能是你的本地hosts文件里的内容出现了问题</code></pre>\n\n<p>首先打开你的**访达                  **<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/08ece50667594a3698471b638819fd43.png\"></p>\n<p>快捷键Shift+Command+G查找文件，输入 <strong>&#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts</strong> ，点击回车</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">![](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;img-blog.csdnimg.cn&#x2F;59c9eaac4fa04ee58024113f5d9c7099.png)![]( &quot;点击并拖拽以移动&quot;)**编辑**</code></pre>\n\n<p>接下来能够看到这样一个文件<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/8ab52d43efd04979bc79b322665a72a7.png\"></p>\n<p>双击打开查看</p>\n<p>如果 与下图区别很大</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/716e5e64f3814c3990f7b4e0e3f943d5.jpeg\"></p>\n<p>**那么问题应该就是出现在这里。接下来打开终端输入 **</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>** sudo -s**</p></blockquote>\n<p>输入密码。 回车</p>\n<p><strong>将下面的内容全部复制并粘贴到前面的终端窗口中，回车确认。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>**cat &lt;<EOF > &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts</p>\n<h2 id=\"\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"\"></a></h2><h1 id=\"Host-Database\"><a href=\"#Host-Database\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Host Database\"></a>Host Database</h1><h1 id=\"-1\"><a href=\"#-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"\"></a></h1><h1 id=\"localhost-is-used-to-configure-the-loopback-interface\"><a href=\"#localhost-is-used-to-configure-the-loopback-interface\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"localhost is used to configure the loopback interface\"></a>localhost is used to configure the loopback interface</h1><h1 id=\"when-the-system-is-booting-Do-not-change-this-entry\"><a href=\"#when-the-system-is-booting-Do-not-change-this-entry\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"when the system is booting.  Do not change this entry.\"></a>when the system is booting.  Do not change this entry.</h1><h2 id=\"-2\"><a href=\"#-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"\"></a></h2><p>127.0.0.1       localhost</p>\n<p>255.255.255.255 broadcasthost</p>\n<p>::1             localhost</p>\n<p>EOF**</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>最后再输入改命令到终端中</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>sudo chown root:wheel &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts; sudo chmod 644 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts</strong></p></blockquote>\n<p>再次双击打开hosts，文件内容就被修改为默认，再次进入Clion，就可以debug了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/805604